{"tid":821342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果天竹拆到蝻亞村 耶撚會唔會話係神蹟","createTime":"2018-09-16T02:27:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T06:06:22.000Z","uid":131933,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cac97e0ae2559444c0e9eefdd4e6f0359e21366f","tid":821342,"uid":131933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T02:27:16.000Z","msg":"吹冧圓方個兩棟沉降樓壓去商場或者高鐵是但一邊就神蹟喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到時實有商家加入嘈鳩政府同大陸工程<br />\n唔洗再得班窮撚基層吠<br />\n雨革佔中佔旺已經證明冇撚用<br />\n而家反共聲音同共鳴每況愈下<br />\n大家都開始習慣比人侵佔<br />\n人人淨係呻兩句然後又一日<br />\n早幾年既怨氣開始消散 已經玩撚完<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇見過革命係講下就可以推翻政權<br />\n一日唔死人一日都唔會有機會成事<br />\n香港人組織唔到一次大型流血衝突就聽天由命喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e48d3d5011d0082db64d8519e809dc5a0f7be2f","tid":821342,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T02:28:54.000Z","msg":"Jihad<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3f7139c8cf92d076a1b5243c097332b279d26e5","tid":821342,"uid":208275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T04:04:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"069e22acbad695a69b2c530c2a21963b4e53fdcc","tid":821342,"uid":131933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e48d3d5011d0082db64d8519e809dc5a0f7be2f","tid":821342,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T02:28:54.000Z","msg":"Jihad<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T04:12:50.000Z","msg":"天收"},{"pid":"62fe681c5650bca2c2aa608cf51289b1d809ba3b","tid":821342,"uid":131933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,